(389, 14, 'President Trump is closing a China trade deal that&#039;s four decades overdue', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/444064-president-trump-is-closing-a-china-trade-deal-thats-four\n', 'As a Main Street entrepreneur, I believe in free trade. But my experience as a business owner also showed me the dire threat China poses to the American economic system: that’s why I have President Trump’s back as he closes the deal with China...', '2019-05-16 18:15:07', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(390, 14, 'Calling out Code Pink&#039;s ignorance and hypocrisy', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/443275-calling-out-code-pinks-ignorance-and-hypocrisy\n', 'The radical leftist group Code Pink got a well-earned taste of what life is like under the oppressive dictator Nicolas Maduro this week, when utilities to the Venezuelan Embassy were shut off. Code Pink has been illegally squatting in the Embassy in...', '2019-05-12 11:45:06', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(391, 14, 'Taiwan&#039;s ability to share health care advances stymied by exclusion from WHO', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/443108-taiwans-ability-to-share-health-care-advances-stymied-by\n', 'In February, an American student Kevin Bozeat shared on his Facebook page his amazing medical experience while studying in Taiwan. Kevin had no health insurance there but still received high-quality and affordable medical care. His story attracted...', '2019-05-10 13:50:08', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(392, 14, 'FDR must be turning in his grave at Trump&#039;s intransigent foreign and trade policy', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/442900-fdr-must-be-turning-in-his-grave-at-trumps-intransigent\n', 'On 26 April, in a fiery speech at the annual meeting of the National Rifle association, President Donald Trump announced the United States\' intention to withdraw as a signatory of the Arms Trade Treaty regulating conventional weapons, a key...', '2019-05-09 13:20:07', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(393, 14, 'Trump&#039;s misguided assault on the Arms Trade Treaty', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/442283-trumps-misguided-assault-on-the-arms-trade-treaty\n', 'During a speech to the National Rifle Association in April, Donald Trump announced that he will “unsign” the United Nations Arms Trade Treaty and ask the Senate to halt the ratification process. Though Trump and other critics argue that...', '2019-05-06 15:15:06', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(394, 14, 'Egypt, our forgotten friend', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/441469-egypt-our-forgotten-friend\n', 'Several years ago, I traveled to Cairo for meetings with Egypt’s president and other prominent government and religious leaders. As my plane approached the country, I watched as the Mediterranean Sea touched the shore of the ancient land. ...', '2019-04-30 20:25:06', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(395, 14, 'As Ukrainians go to the polls, the US supports the nation against malevolent influence from Russia', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/439713-as-ukrainians-go-to-the-polls-the-us-supports-the-nation\n', 'On April 21, the people of Ukraine will go to the polls to choose their next president.No matter the outcome, the United States stands ready to support the Ukrainian people against foreign actors seeking to undermine Ukraine’s democratic trajectory...', '2019-04-19 12:57:07', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(396, 14, 'Four decades of the Taiwan Relations Act remains a monument to our resolve to uphold democracy', 'https://thehill.com/blogs/congress-blog/foreign-policy/438090-four-decades-of-the-taiwan-relations-act-remains-a\n', 'In 1979, the cost of a gallon of gas was 86 cents. Atari was the “must-have” electronic system, costing consumers around $200, and my team, the Cincinnati Reds claimed their sixth National League West Division title.In political news, on...', '2019-04-10 10:15:05', '2019-06-22 20:36:43', '2019-06-22 20:36:43'),
(398, 15, 'London’s Other Royal Observatory', 'https://lookup.london/kings-observatory/', '<p>You\'ve probably heard of the Royal Observatory in Greenwich, but there\'s also the King\'s Observatory in Richmond. Join me for a look around...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/kings-observatory/\">London&#8217;s Other Royal Observatory</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-06-11 19:56:47', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(399, 15, 'The Dog and Bowl Sculpture Outside Southwark Station', 'https://lookup.london/dog-sculpture-southwark/', '<p>Look up outside Southwark station and you\'ll see a dog licking a bowl. But why is it there?</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/dog-sculpture-southwark/\">The Dog and Bowl Sculpture Outside Southwark Station</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-06-04 18:43:34', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(400, 15, 'London’s Strangest Statues', 'https://lookup.london/strangest-statues/', '<p>Theres thousands of statues to important and interesting figures in London. But there are some very odd ones too.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/strangest-statues/\">London&#8217;s Strangest Statues</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-05-28 15:22:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(401, 15, 'The Details of Hay’s Wharf, London Bridge', 'https://lookup.london/hays-wharf/', '<p>Walking over London Bridge, I\'ll always take in the views of Tower Bridge and The Shard. However, what really catches my eye is the dirty gold letters exclaiming HAY\'S WHARF.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/hays-wharf/\">The Details of Hay&#8217;s Wharf, London Bridge</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-05-21 14:33:00', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(402, 15, 'The Geeky Hidden Gem at Temple Tube Station', 'https://lookup.london/temple-tube-station/', '<p>Before you enter Temple Tube Station, pause a second to appreciate this heritage tube map. Times certainly have changed...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/temple-tube-station/\">The Geeky Hidden Gem at Temple Tube Station</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-05-14 12:44:03', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(403, 15, 'London’s 9 Strangest Church Steeples', 'https://lookup.london/strangest-church-steeples/', '<p>Today they might be dwarfed by skyscrapers, but that doesn\'t mean they\'re less impressive (or eye-catching!)</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/strangest-church-steeples/\">London&#8217;s 9 Strangest Church Steeples</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-05-07 12:02:03', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(404, 15, 'Behind the Scenes at Charing Cross Station', 'https://lookup.london/charing-cross-station/', '<p>In 1999 a section of Charing Cross Station closed to the public, but there\'s still a way to get behind the scenes and explore the disused tunnels...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/charing-cross-station/\">Behind the Scenes at Charing Cross Station</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-04-29 13:57:10', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(405, 15, 'Lloyd’s Register of Shipping', 'https://lookup.london/lloyds-register/', '<p>A building which gets more exciting the closer you look. From intricate details to the juxtaposition of glass and steel. It even has a small, colourful garden…</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/lloyds-register/\">Lloyd&#8217;s Register of Shipping</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-04-23 16:48:04', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(406, 15, 'A Secret Garden in Southwark | Red Cross Garden', 'https://lookup.london/red-cross-garden/', '<p>A gem of a garden in Southwark, with plenty of history too!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/red-cross-garden/\">A Secret Garden in Southwark | Red Cross Garden</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-04-15 16:37:42', '2019-06-22 20:36:54', '2019-06-22 20:36:54'),
(407, 15, 'The Secret History Under Liverpool Street Station', 'https://lookup.london/history-under-liverpool-street/', '<p>Walking through the modern station today, it\'s hard to believe the history hiding underneath Liverpool Street. That is until you know where to look...</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london/history-under-liverpool-street/\">The Secret History Under Liverpool Street Station</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://lookup.london\">Look Up London Tours</a>.</p>\n', '2019-06-18 16:29:00', '2019-06-22 21:09:40', '2019-06-22 21:09:40'),
(408, 1, 'Are employers overlooking the potential of an ageing workforce?', 'https://blog.totaljobs.com/are-employers-overlooking-the-potential-of-an-ageing-workforce', '<p>The <a href=\"http://press.totaljobs.com/release/ageing-workforce-left-on-the-shelf-research-shows-lack-of-opportunities-for-over-50s/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">latest research from Totaljobs and Robert Walters</a> has revealed that three quarters of people in their 50s have never been offered a promotion by their current employer. What’s more, a third are not aware of what they need to do in order to get one.<br />\nThis comes in spite of the ONS estimation that by 2020 one in.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.totaljobs.com/are-employers-overlooking-the-potential-of-an-ageing-workforce\">Are employers overlooking the potential of an ageing workforce?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://blog.totaljobs.com\">Totaljobs Recruiter Blog</a>.</p>\n', '2019-06-11 09:06:31', '2019-06-22 21:20:10', '2019-06-22 21:20:10');

